Class Notification

  • java.lang.Object
    • team21.pylonconstructor.Notification
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Notification>

    public class Notification
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Notification>
    This class is used to represent notifications. Notifications are identified by a id and user and contain info such as taggged by and moodid Notifications are stored on ElasticSearch.
    Version:
    1.0
    See Also:
